{"type":"message","id":"88774828","parentId":"6570b6d1","timestamp":"2026-04-02T14:41:12.219Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_lo9limzpwifjc7av3kw4np48","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/video-frames/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":17623,"output":46,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17669,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775140869452,"responseId":"0217751408696351201fb9e16e3f5837dd939723f94961141dc9e"}}
{"type":"message","id":"697081ed","parentId":"88774828","timestamp":"2026-04-02T14:41:12.259Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_lo9limzpwifjc7av3kw4np48","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: video-frames\ndescription: 使用 ffmpeg 从视频中提取帧或短视频片段.\nhomepage: https://ffmpeg.org\nmetadata: {\"clawdbot\":{\"emoji\":\"🎞️\",\"requires\":{\"bins\":[\"ffmpeg\"]},\"install\":[{\"id\":\"brew\",\"kind\":\"brew\",\"formula\":\"ffmpeg\",\"bins\":[\"ffmpeg\"],\"label\":\"Install ffmpeg (brew)\"}]}}\n---\n\n# Video Frames (ffmpeg)\n\nExtract a single frame from a video, or create quick thumbnails for inspection.\n\n## Quick start\n\nFirst frame:\n\n```bash\n{baseDir}/scripts/frame.sh /path/to/video.mp4 --out /tmp/frame.jpg\n```\n\nAt a timestamp:\n\n```bash\n{baseDir}/scripts/frame.sh /path/to/video.mp4 --time 00:00:10 --out /tmp/frame-10s.jpg\n```\n\n## Notes\n\n- Prefer `--time` for “what is happening around here?”.\n- Use a `.jpg` for quick share; use `.png` for crisp UI frames.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775140872254}}
{"type":"message","id":"f736846f","parentId":"697081ed","timestamp":"2026-04-02T14:41:14.724Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"你说的是「video-frames」这个技能吧？它已经安装在你的本地 workspace 里了 🎞️\n\n这个技能使用 ffmpeg 从视频中提取帧或短视频片段，支持：\n- 提取视频第一帧\n- 按指定时间戳提取特定帧\n- 提取多个帧序列\n- 裁剪短视频片段\n\n如果你需要使用这个技能，直接告诉我你想处理哪个视频，我来帮你操作～\n\n你是想提取视频帧还是截取片段呢？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":10955,"output":109,"cacheRead":6968,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18032,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775140872260,"responseId":"0217751408724501201fb9e16e3f5837dd939723f949611f5d4dc"}}
