{"type":"message","id":"76b9c9d1","parentId":"6025d862","timestamp":"2026-04-02T14:48:51.656Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我看到已经有 `openai-whisper` 和 `openai-whisper-api` 了，你想要添加的 `whisper-transcribe` 和它们有什么区别吗？让我先看看 `openai-whisper` 的 SKILL：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_l863ronghmpmaiu9asn47h7e","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.nvm/versions/node/v23.11.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/openai-whisper/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":1919,"output":118,"cacheRead":20280,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22317,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775141329098,"responseId":"0217751413293252748f57c5f4210b3bc611acce6828c7a124b67"}}
{"type":"message","id":"da723728","parentId":"76b9c9d1","timestamp":"2026-04-02T14:48:51.692Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_l863ronghmpmaiu9asn47h7e","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: openai-whisper\ndescription: Local speech-to-text with the Whisper CLI (no API key).\nhomepage: https://openai.com/research/whisper\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\":\n      {\n        \"emoji\": \"🎤\",\n        \"requires\": { \"bins\": [\"whisper\"] },\n        \"install\":\n          [\n            {\n              \"id\": \"brew\",\n              \"kind\": \"brew\",\n              \"formula\": \"openai-whisper\",\n              \"bins\": [\"whisper\"],\n              \"label\": \"Install OpenAI Whisper (brew)\",\n            },\n          ],\n      },\n  }\n---\n\n# Whisper (CLI)\n\nUse `whisper` to transcribe audio locally.\n\nQuick start\n\n- `whisper /path/audio.mp3 --model medium --output_format txt --output_dir .`\n- `whisper /path/audio.m4a --task translate --output_format srt`\n\nNotes\n\n- Models download to `~/.cache/whisper` on first run.\n- `--model` defaults to `turbo` on this install.\n- Use smaller models for speed, larger for accuracy.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775141331687}}
{"type":"message","id":"c758802f","parentId":"da723728","timestamp":"2026-04-02T14:48:56.016Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"明白了，原来已经有 `openai-whisper` 技能了，它也是用 Whisper CLI 在本地转录音频，和你本地的 `whisper-transcribe` 功能类似。你看：\n\n**已存在的 openai-whisper (官方技能):**\n- 位置：`~/.nvm/versions/node/v23.11.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/openai-whisper/`\n- 功能：使用 `whisper` 命令行工具在本地进行语音转文字，支持多种输出格式\n- 已经在技能列表里了\n\n**你的 whisper-transcribe:**\n- 位置：`~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/whisper-transcribe/`\n- 功能类似，也是封装 Whisper CLI\n\n你想要我怎么做？\n\n1. **把你本地的 whisper-transcribe 软链接到系统技能目录**，这样它就会出现在技能列表里\n2. **直接使用已有的 openai-whisper 技能**，功能已经够用了\n3. **对比一下**，看看哪个更适合你的需求"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":781,"output":239,"cacheRead":21816,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22836,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775141331692,"responseId":"0217751413319202748f57c5f4210b3bc611acce6828c7a1cbdcf"}}
