{"type":"compaction","id":"ef0d65f4","parentId":"d64a72fb","timestamp":"2026-04-02T15:01:55.393Z","summary":"## Decisions\nNo decisions made yet.\n\n## Open TODOs\n- Determine if user wants to extract video frames or截取 video clips, then perform the requested processing.\n\n## Constraints/Rules\nNone.\n\n## Pending user asks\n- User has not yet answered whether they want to extract video frames or截取 video segments, or specified the target video to process.\n\n## Exact identifiers\n- Query: `视频提取帧 视频提取片段 技能`\n- Skill file path: `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/video-frames/SKILL.md`\n- Script path pattern: `{baseDir}/scripts/frame.sh`\n- Homepage: `https://ffmpeg.org`\n- Required binary: `ffmpeg`\n- Brew install formula: `ffmpeg`\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Decisions\n- **(No decisions made yet)**: The assistant is still gathering information to fulfill the user's request.\n\n## Open TODOs\n- Add `openclaw-control-ui` (label: `openclaw-control-ui`, id: `openclaw-control-ui`) to the OpenClaw skills list.\n- Clarify the difference between the user's `whisper-transcribe` skill and the existing `openai-whisper`/`openai-whisper-api` skills in the OpenClaw skills directory.\n\n## Constraints/Rules\n- **(none)**\n\n## Pending user asks\n1. Add `openclaw-control-ui` to the OpenClaw skills list.\n2. (Pending clarification): Explain if/how `whisper-transcribe` differs from existing `openai-whisper`/`openai-whisper-api` skills.\n\n## Exact identifiers\n- Date/Time: `[Thu 2026-04-02 22:48 GMT+8]`\n- Metadata: `{\"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\", \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"}`\n- File paths:\n  - `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/skills/whisper-transcribe/SKILL.md`\n  - `~/.nvm/versions/node/v23.11.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/`\n  - `~/.nvm/versions/node/v23.11.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/openai-whisper/SKILL.md`\n- Existing skill names: `1password`, `apple-notes`, `apple-reminders`, `bear-notes`, `blogwatcher`, `blucli`, `bluebubbles`, `camsnap`, `canvas`, `clawhub`, `coding-agent`, `discord`, `eightctl`, `gemini`, `gh-issues`, `gifgrep`, `github`, `gog`, `goplaces`, `healthcheck`, `himalaya`, `imsg`, `mcporter`, `model-usage`, `nano-pdf`, `node-connect`, `notion`, `obsidian`, `openai-whisper`, `openai-whisper-api`\n\n## Recent turns preserved verbatim\n- User: Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Thu 2026-04-02 22:41 GMT+8] Whisper Transcribe 我在技能列表里怎么没找到这个技能\n- User: Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Thu 2026-04-02 22:45 GMT+8] 不是这个技能，是whisper-transcribe这个技能\n- Assistant: [non-text content: toolCall]\n- Tool result (memory_search): {\n  \"results\": [],\n  \"provider\": \"none\",\n  \"citations\": \"auto\",\n  \"mode\": \"fts-only\"\n}\n- Assistant: [non-text content: toolCall]\n- Tool result (exec): total 16\ndrwxr-xr-x@  8 liuchenglong  staff   256 Apr  1 17:04 .\ndrwxr-xr-x@ 36 liuchenglong  staff  1152 Apr  2 08:11 ..\n-rw-r--r--@  1 liuchenglong  staff  6148 Mar 21 22:37 .DS_Store\ndrwx------@  4 liuchenglong  staff   128 Mar 30 23:39 agent-browser-clawdbot-0.1.0\ndrwxr-xr-x  10 liuchenglong  staff   320 Apr  1 15:43 multimodal-quiz-generator\ndrwx------@  5 liuchenglong  staff   160 Mar 21 21:49 video-frames\ndrwx------@  7 liuchenglong  staff   224 Mar 21 21:40 video-gen\ndrwx------@  6 liuchenglong  staff   192 Apr  1 17:05 whisper-transcribe\n- Assistant: 找到了，`whisper-transcribe` 确实已经安装在本地了，位置是 `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/whisper-transcribe/`。让我看看它的 SKILL.md：\n[non-text content: toolCall]\n- Tool result (read): # Whisper Transcribe Skill\n\n使用 OpenAI Whisper 从音视频文件中提取文本，支持纯文本输出和带时间戳的 VTT/SRT 字幕格式。\n\n## Description\n\n本技能封装了 Whisper 命令行工具，提供便捷的音视频转录功能：\n\n- 支持常见音视频格式（mp3, wav, flac, mp4, m4a 等）\n- 可指定输出格式：纯文本(txt)、VTT字幕、SRT字幕、JSON、TSV\n- 支持手动指定语言，默认自动检测\n- 支持不同模型大小（tiny, base, small, medium, large）\n- 输出文件自动保存在当前工作目录\n\n## Usage\n\n```\n当用户需要从音视频中提取文字或生成字幕时，使用此技能。\n\nExamples:\n- \"帮我把这个 MP3 转成文字\"\n- \"提取这个视频的字幕，要带时间戳\"\n- \"用 whisper 转录这个音频，输出 vtt 格式\"\n```\n\n## Parameters\n\n- `input_file`: 输入音视频文件路径（必填）\n- `output_format`: 输出格式，可选 `txt`, `vtt`, `srt`, `json`, `tsv`, `all`，默认 `all`\n- `language`: 语言代码，例如 `zh`, `en`, `ja`，默认自动检测\n- ...\n- Assistant: 找到了！`whisper-transcribe` 技能确实已经安装在你的本地了 ✅\n\n位置在：`~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/whisper-transcribe/`\n\n这个技能使用 OpenAI Whisper 从音视频文件中提取文本，支持：\n- 多种音视频格式（mp3, wav, flac, mp4, m4a 等）\n- 多种输出格式：纯文本(txt)、VTT字幕、SRT字幕、JSON、TSV\n- 自动检测语言，也可手动指定\n- 支持不同模型大小（tiny, base, small, medium, large）\n\n为什么在技能列表里没找到？可能是因为它是你手动添加到 workspace 的，而不是通过 ClawHub 安装的。OpenClaw 默认从 `~/.nvm/versions/node/v23.11.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/` 读取技能列表。\n\n你需要现在用它转录音视频吗？把文件发给我，我来帮你处理～\n\n<read-files>\n/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/skills/whisper-transcribe/SKILL.md\n~/.nvm/versions/node/v23.11.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/openai-whisper/SKILL.md\n~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/video-frames/SKILL.md\n~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/whisper-transcribe/SKILL.md\n\n</read-files>","firstKeptEntryId":"c758802f","tokensBefore":27376,"details":{"readFiles":["/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/skills/whisper-transcribe/SKILL.md","~/.nvm/versions/node/v23.11.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/openai-whisper/SKILL.md","~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/video-frames/SKILL.md","~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/whisper-transcribe/SKILL.md"],"modifiedFiles":[]},"fromHook":true}
