{"type":"message","id":"ce5254ed","parentId":"a6de248a","timestamp":"2026-04-02T15:02:05.408Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我看到了！在输出中我发现了这个警告：`[skills] Skipping skill path that resolves outside its configured root.`\n\n这就是问题所在！OpenClaw 默认不允许加载配置根目录之外的技能。由于我们是软链接到系统目录，但实际文件在你的 `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills`，它超出了 OpenClaw 的根目录范围，所以被跳过了。\n\n让我看看完整的技能列表后半部分，确认一下：\n\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2xrj7roxr6yf0iyeyy7s9ko8","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw skills | tail -n +80"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":8801,"output":147,"cacheRead":17208,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26156,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775142120600,"responseId":"021775142120848336c0ccc8833e375a271994f02c20b09172046"}}
