{"type":"message","id":"3090d0a8","parentId":"a774ac70","timestamp":"2026-04-02T15:02:19.008Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"目录权限是正常的。让我看看 SKILL.md 的格式有没有问题，是不是缺少了一些必填字段？对比一下其他 workspace 技能：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_gtdgq0i4j01wzwkxt8g7gzim","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/video-frames/SKILL.md","limit":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":22644,"output":92,"cacheRead":3896,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26632,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775142136156,"responseId":"021775142136414336c0ccc8833e375a271994f02c20b09c3ff00"}}
{"type":"message","id":"15158f8c","parentId":"3090d0a8","timestamp":"2026-04-02T15:02:19.047Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_gtdgq0i4j01wzwkxt8g7gzim","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: video-frames\ndescription: 使用 ffmpeg 从视频中提取帧或短视频片段.\nhomepage: https://ffmpeg.org\nmetadata: {\"clawdbot\":{\"emoji\":\"🎞️\",\"requires\":{\"bins\":[\"ffmpeg\"]},\"install\":[{\"id\":\"brew\",\"kind\":\"brew\",\"formula\":\"ffmpeg\",\"bins\":[\"ffmpeg\"],\"label\":\"Install ffmpeg (brew)\"}]}}\n---\n\n# Video Frames (ffmpeg)\n\nExtract a single frame from a video, or create quick thumbnails for inspection.\n\n## Quick start\n\nFirst frame:\n\n```bash\n{baseDir}/scripts/frame.sh /path/to/video.mp4 --out /tmp/frame.jpg\n```\n\nAt a timestamp:\n\n```bash\n{baseDir}/scripts/frame.sh /path/to/video.mp4 --time 00:00:10 --out /tmp/frame-10s.jpg\n```\n\n## Notes\n\n- Prefer `--time` for “what is happening around here?”.\n- Use a `.jpg` for quick share; use `.png` for crisp UI frames.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775142139040}}
{"type":"message","id":"d7d5b819","parentId":"15158f8c","timestamp":"2026-04-02T15:02:25.466Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"找到问题了！💡\n\n你的 `whisper-transcribe/SKILL.md` 缺少开头的 YAML front matter，里面需要包含 `name` 和 `description` 等元数据。对比一下 `video-frames`，它开头就有正确的格式：\n\n```yaml\n---\nname: video-frames\ndescription: 使用 ffmpeg 从视频中提取帧或短视频片段.\nhomepage: https://ffmpeg.org\nmetadata: {\"clawdbot\":{\"emoji\":\"🎞️\",\"requires\":{\"bins\":[\"ffmpeg\"]},\"install\":[{\"id\":\"brew\",\"kind\":\"brew\",\"formula\":\"ffmpeg\",\"bins\":[\"ffmpeg\"],\"label\":\"Install ffmpeg (brew)\"}]}}\n---\n```\n\n让我给你的 `whisper-transcribe/SKILL.md` 添加正确的 front matter：\n\n\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_xto49hdei25u6fd3vpw1tst1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/whisper-transcribe/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":461,"output":229,"cacheRead":26424,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":27114,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775142139048,"responseId":"021775142139307336c0ccc8833e375a271994f02c20b09b31d67"}}
{"type":"message","id":"ada53928","parentId":"d7d5b819","timestamp":"2026-04-02T15:02:25.498Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_xto49hdei25u6fd3vpw1tst1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Whisper Transcribe Skill\n\n使用 OpenAI Whisper 从音视频文件中提取文本，支持纯文本输出和带时间戳的 VTT/SRT 字幕格式。\n\n## Description\n\n本技能封装了 Whisper 命令行工具，提供便捷的音视频转录功能：\n\n- 支持常见音视频格式（mp3, wav, flac, mp4, m4a 等）\n- 可指定输出格式：纯文本(txt)、VTT字幕、SRT字幕、JSON、TSV\n- 支持手动指定语言，默认自动检测\n- 支持不同模型大小（tiny, base, small, medium, large）\n- 输出文件自动保存在当前工作目录\n\n## Usage\n\n```\n当用户需要从音视频中提取文字或生成字幕时，使用此技能。\n\nExamples:\n- \"帮我把这个 MP3 转成文字\"\n- \"提取这个视频的字幕，要带时间戳\"\n- \"用 whisper 转录这个音频，输出 vtt 格式\"\n```\n\n## Parameters\n\n- `input_file`: 输入音视频文件路径（必填）\n- `output_format`: 输出格式，可选 `txt`, `vtt`, `srt`, `json`, `tsv`, `all`，默认 `all`\n- `language`: 语言代码，例如 `zh`, `en`, `ja`，默认自动检测\n- `model`: 模型大小，可选 `tiny`, `base`, `small`, `medium`, `large`，默认 `medium`（中文推荐 medium 或 large）\n\n## Requirements\n\n- Whisper 命令行工具已安装 (`pip install openai-whisper`)\n- FFmpeg 已安装（用于处理音视频）\n- 模型会自动下载，需要网络连接\n\n## Examples\n\n### 示例 1：默认转录（输出所有格式，中文 medium 模型）\n\n```\ntranscribe /path/to/audio.mp3 --language zh\n```\n\n### 示例 2：只输出带时间戳的 VTT 格式\n\n```\ntranscribe /path/to/video.mp4 --output_format vtt --language zh\n```\n\n### 示例 3：使用大模型获得更高准确率\n\n```\ntranscribe /path/to/audio.mp3 --output_format all --language zh --model large\n```\n\n## Notes\n\n- 模型越大准确率越高，但速度越慢：\n  - `tiny` ~1GB 内存，最快\n  - `base` ~1GB 内存\n  - `small` ~2GB 内存\n  - `medium` ~5GB 内存\n  - `large` ~10GB 内存，最慢但最准确\n- 中文建议使用 `medium` 以上模型，准确率较好\n- 首次使用会自动下载模型文件，需要等待\n\n## Author\n\nCreated by user request\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775142145492}}
