{"type":"compaction","id":"96557b6a","parentId":"76ebfc42","timestamp":"2026-04-02T15:06:22.830Z","summary":"## Decisions\n- **(No decisions made yet)**: The assistant is still gathering information to fulfill the user's request after creating the softlink.\n\n## Open TODOs\n- Add `openclaw-control-ui` (label: `openclaw-control-ui`, id: `openclaw-control-ui`) to the OpenClaw skills list.\n- Clarify the difference between the user's `whisper-transcribe` skill and the existing `openai-whisper`/`openai-whisper-api` skills in the OpenClaw skills directory.\n\n## Constraints/Rules\n- **(none)**\n\n## Pending user asks\n1. Add `openclaw-control-ui` to the OpenClaw skills list.\n2. (Pending clarification): Explain if/how `whisper-transcribe` differs from existing `openai-whisper`/`openai-whisper-api` skills, and confirm what the user wants to do next with `whisper-transcribe`.\n\n## Exact identifiers\n- Date/Time: `[Thu 2026-04-02 22:48 GMT+8]`\n- Metadata: `{\"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\", \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"}`\n- File paths:\n  - `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/skills/whisper-transcribe/SKILL.md`\n  - `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/whisper-transcribe/`\n  - `~/.nvm/versions/node/v23.11.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/`\n  - `~/.nvm/versions/node/v23.11.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/openai-whisper/`\n  - `~/.nvm/versions/node/v23.11.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/openai-whisper/SKILL.md`\n  - `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/video-frames/SKILL.md`\n- Existing skill names: `1password`, `apple-notes`, `apple-reminders`, `bear-notes`, `blogwatcher`, `blucli`, `bluebubbles`, `camsnap`, `canvas`, `clawhub`, `coding-agent`, `discord`, `eightctl`, `gemini`, `gh-issues`, `gifgrep`, `github`, `gog`, `goplaces`, `healthcheck`, `himalaya`, `imsg`, `mcporter`, `model-usage`, `nano-pdf`, `node-connect`, `notion`, `obsidian`, `openai-whisper`, `openai-whisper-api`\n- Executed command: `ln -s ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/whisper-transcribe ~/.nvm/versions/node/v23.11.1/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/whisper-transcribe`\n- Tool result: `(no output)`\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Decisions\n- **Add local skill directory to configuration**: It was determined that adding `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/` to `skills.load.extraDirs` would allow loading all local skills, which would resolve the issue of `openclaw-control-ui` not being visible.\n\n## Open TODOs\n- Complete troubleshooting of why the `openclaw-control-ui` skill cannot be seen\n- Check OpenClaw's skill reading behavior and whether additional skill paths need configuration\n- Look up the configuration schema for the `skills` section to resolve config validation errors\n- Retrieve the full current openclaw configuration from `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/openclaw.json`\n- Retrieve the current `skills` configuration via `gateway(action=\"config.get\", path=\"skills\")`\n- Fix configuration patching errors to successfully add the local skills directory\n\n## Constraints/Rules\n- For `gateway` `config.patch` action, the `raw` parameter must be a string, cannot be a JSON object (original rule)\n- `config.patch` requires the `raw` parameter to be an object, not an array (updated rule)\n- Configuration schema validation rejects unrecognized keys at the specified path\n\n## Pending user asks\n- User reports that `openclaw-control-ui` is still not visible, waiting for continued troubleshooting\n\n## Exact identifiers\n- Skill ID/label: `openclaw-control-ui`\n- Timestamp 1: [Thu 2026-04-02 22:57 GMT+8]\n- Checked directory path: `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/whisper-transcribe/`\n- Files in checked directory: `README.md`, `SKILL.md`, `package.json`, `scripts/`\n- Gateway actions called: `config.get`, `config.patch`, `config.schema.lookup`\n- Config file path: `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/openclaw.json`\n- Config exists: `true`\n- Config auth profiles: `moonshot:default`, `zhipu:default`\n- Moonshot base URL: `https://api.moonshot.cn/v1`\n- Moonshot model ID: `kimi-k2.5`\n- Zhipu base URL: `https://open.bigmodel.cn/api/paas/v4`\n- Zhipu model IDs: `glm-4-flash`, `glm-4-plus`\n- 32649 additional characters of config content truncated\n- Config path attempted (initial): `skills.entries.whisper-transcribe`\n- Config path for schema lookup: `skills`, `skills.load`\n- Target config path: `skills.load.extraDirs`\n- Config paths: `/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/openclaw.json`, `skills`, `skills.load`, `skills.load.extraDirs`, `skills.load.watch`, `skills.load.watchDebounceMs`, `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/`\n- Timestamps: `2026.3.28`, `2026-04-01T03:29:41.127Z`, `2026-03-21T04:21:52.324Z`, `2026.3.13`\n- Providers: `moonshot`, `zhipu`\n- Model names: `Kimi K2.5`, `GLM-4-Flash`, `GLM-4-Plus`\n- API types: `openai-completions`\n- Tool calls: `gateway(action=\"config.schema.lookup\", path=\"skills.load\")`, `gateway(action=\"config.patch\", path=\"skills.load.extraDirs\", raw=\"[\\\"~/.openclaw/workspace/skills\\\"]\", note=\"Add local workspace skills directory to extraDirs\")`, `gateway(action=\"config.patch\", path=\"skills.load\", raw=\"{\\\"extraDirs\\\": [\\\"~/.openclaw/workspace/skills\\\"]}\", note=\"Add local workspace skills directory to extraDirs\")`, `gateway(action=\"config.get\", path=\"skills\")`\n- Errors: \n  1. First `config.patch` error: `Validation failed for tool \"gateway\": - raw: must be string`\n  2. Second `config.patch` error: `invalid config: <root>: Unrecognized key: \"enabled\"`\n  3. Third `config.patch` error: `Validation failed for tool \"gateway\": - raw: must be string`\n  4. Fourth `config.patch` error: `invalid config: <root>: Unrecognized key: \"entries\"`\n  5. `config.patch raw must be an object.`\n  6. `invalid config: <root>: Unrecognized key: \"extraDirs\"`\n\n## Recent turns preserved verbatim\n- User: Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Thu 2026-04-02 22:49 GMT+8] 本地的 whisper-transcribe 软链接到系统